            <div type="transcript" id="P91-6">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Hope is the thing with feathers</l>
                    <l>That perches in the soul,</l>
                    <l>And sings the tune without the words,</l>
                    <l>And never stops at all,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And sweetest in the gale is heard;</l>
                    <l>And sore must be the storm</l>
                    <l>That could abash the little bird</l>
                    <l>That kept so many warm.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I 've heard it in the chillest land,</l>
                    <l>And on the strangest sea;</l>
                    <l>Yet, never, in extremity,</l>
                    <l>It asked a crumb of me.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
